0px; text-align: justify;">Double Sum Assured, in case of accidental death&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0.35em 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; text-align: justify;"><strong>Additional Benefits:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="margin: 0.35em 0px 0.8em; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n	<li style="margin: 0.3em 0px 0.3em 1.6em; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Tax Benefit</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0.3em 0px 0.3em 1.6em; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Surrender after 1 year</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0.3em 0px 0.3em 1.6em; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Loan facility</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0.3em 0px 0.3em 1.6em; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Ownership can be handed over to any Bank or Financial institution</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Contents Page', 30, '2015-01-06', 'No', '73.jpg', 'normal', 'No', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
