ye sight</font></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#cccccc" valign="top">100% of Sum Assured</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#0066ff" class="w" valign="top"><font color="#ffffff">Loss of wrist or one hand above wrist; loss of ankle or one leg above ankle</font></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#cccccc" valign="top">100% of Sum Assured</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#0066ff" class="w" valign="top"><font color="#ffffff">Loss of wrist or one hand above wrist; loss of ankle or one leg above ankle &amp; permanent loss of one eye sight</font></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#cccccc" valign="top">100% of Sum Assured</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#0066ff" class="w" valign="top"><font color="#ffffff">Permanent loss of ear hearing</font></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#cccccc" valign="top">50% of Sum Assured</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#0066ff" class="w" valign="top"><font color="#ffffff">Loss of wrist or one hand above wrist; loss of ankle or one leg above ankle</font></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#cccccc" valign="top">50% of Sum Assured</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#0066ff" class="w" valign="top"><font color="#ffffff">Permanent loss of sight of one eye</font></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#cccccc" valign="top">50% of Sum Assured</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class="article_separator" style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); display:block; font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px; height:1.5em; line-height:18px">&nbsp;</span>', 'Contents Page', 40, '2015-01-06', 'No', '81.jpg', 'normal', 'No', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
