(341, 'Childs Marriage and Educational Endowment Plan', 'childs-marriage-and-educational-endowment-plan', 'Menu', 335, '', 'This is an Endowment Assurance with profit plan that provides lumpsum on maturity date to meet the Educational /Marriage expenses of the children. In case of untimely death of the Assured, no further premium will be payable. All the benefits shall be paid on the maturity as per policy terms and conditions.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nPolicy Requirements<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Minimum Entry Age&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : 17 Years<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Maximum Entry Age &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;: 60 Years<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Maximum Maturity Age &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;: 65 Years<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Minimum Term Period &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;: 5 Years<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Maximum Term Period &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; : 25 Years<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Minimum Sum Assured &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;: Rs. 10,000/-<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Maximum Sum Assured &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; : As per income source<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Premium Payment Frequency &nbsp; : Yearly, Half Yearly, Quarterly and Monthly<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Nominee (child) age &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;: Till age 16 yrs<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Age Computation&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Age next birthday<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Policy Benefits:</strong><br />\r\nOn Maturity&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Sum Assured plus bonus earned<br />\r\nOn Death&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Premium waived till maturity<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Sum Assured plus bonus earned is paid to the nominee (child) on maturity<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>&nbsp;Rider Benefits:</strong><br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Accidental Death Benefit (ADB) up to Rs. 2,500,000.00 in additional Rs. 1.00 per thousand.<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Waiver of Premium (WOP) benefit shall be taken in additional Rs. 2.00 per thousand.<br />\r\nOther benefits:<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Paid up and surrender claim shall be provided<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Loan Facility provided.<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tax exemption as per ITA,2058<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Rs. 1 Rebate is provided', 'Contents Page', 10, '2015-06-08', 'No', '341.jpg', 'normal', 'No', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(342, 'Bal Amrit', 'bal-amrit1', 'Menu', 335, '', 'This policy is Endowment Assurance with profit plan designed to provide education and other expenses of the child in case of death of the proposer.<br />\r\n<strong>Policy Requirements</strong><br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Entry age&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : New born to 15 Years<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Proposer Entry Age&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : 20 to 50 Years<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Minimum Policy Term &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : 11 Years<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Maximum Policy Term&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : 20 Years<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Minimum Sum Assured&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Rs. 50,000/-<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Maximum Sum Assured &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Rs. 2,500,000/-<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Premium Payment Frequency : Yearly, Half Yearly, Quarterly, monthly<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Proposer &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Mother, Father or Legal Guardian<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Age computation&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Age next birthday<br />\r\n<strong>Risk Commencement</strong><br />\r\nProposer&#39;s risk will be covered from the commencement of policy.<br />\r\nAssured risk will be covered at the age six and two years after commencement of policy.<br />\r\n<strong>Payment Benefit: on active policy</strong><br />\r\n<u>On the survival of Assured (Child)</u><br />\r\nSum Assured plus bonus on maturity<br />\r\n<u>On the death of Assured (Child)</u><br />\r\nDeath before commencement of risk, paid premium with 3% annual interest will be paid<br />\r\n<span style="line-height:20.8px">On death after commencement of risk, sum assured plus bonus will be paid</span><br />\r\n<strong>Proposer&#39;s (on active policy)</strong><br />\r\nIn case of death of proposer, 20% of the sum assured shall be provided to the assured<br />\r\nPremiums are waived on death/disablement of the proposer and thereafter 1% of the sum insured is paid as monthly income to the child till attainment of specified age.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nOn maturity there shall be a payment of lumsum amount of sum insured together with bonus, where the proposer is alive or not.<br />\r\n&nbsp;Accidental death benefit(ADB) is not applicable<br />\r\n<strong>Other benefits:</strong><br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Paid up and surrender claim shall be provided<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Loan Facility provided.<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tax exemption as per ITA,2058<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;', 'Normal Group', 20, '2015-06-08', 'No', '342.jpg', 'normal', 'No', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(343, 'Bal Bhagyodaya (Anticipated Endowment)', 'bal-bhagyodaya-anticipated-endowment1', 'Menu', 335, '', '<br />\r\nIt is anticipated endowment with profit plan, specifically designed to take care of the educational needs of children for a specific term of 15 years. As an anticipated plan, benefits under the plan are payable at specified installment irrespective of whether the Life Assured survives to the end of the policy term or dies during the term of the policy. Premium is waived in case of death of the Assured.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nPolicy Requirements<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Minimum Entry Age &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; : 17 Years<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Maximum Entry Age&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : 50 Years<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Maximum Maturity Age &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; : 65 Years<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Term Period &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; : 15 Years<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Minimum Sum Assured &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Rs. 25,000/-<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Maximum Sum Assured &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : As per income source<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Premium Payment Frequency &nbsp; &nbsp; : Yearly, Half Yearly, Quarterly and Monthly<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Nominee (child) age &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;:Till age 16 yrs<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Age computation&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Age next birthday<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Rs. 1 rebate is provided<br />\r\n<strong>Policy Benefits:</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Survival Benefits:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>25% of Sum Assured after completion of first 5 years</li>\r\n	<li>25% of Sum Assured after completion of second 5 years</li>\r\n	<li>50% of Sum Assured plus bonus on maturity</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Death Benefits:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Premium payment shall be waived till maturity</li>\r\n	<li>Regular anticipated installment shall be paid even after the death of assured</li>\r\n	<li>50% of Sum Assured plus Entire bonus earned shall be paid to the nominee (child) on maturity</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>&nbsp;Rider Benefits:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Accidental Death Benefit (ADB) up to Rs. 2,500,000.00 in additional Rs. 1.00 per thousand.</li>\r\n	<li>Waiver of Premium (WOP) benefit shall be taken in additional Rs. 2.00 per thousand.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Other benefits:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Paid up and surrender claim shall be provided</li>\r\n	<li>Loan Facility provided.</li>\r\n	<li>Tax exemption as per ITA,2058</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Normal Group', 30, '2015-06-08', 'No', '343.jpg', 'normal', 'No', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(344, 'Traditional Endowment Assurance Policy', 'traditional-endowment-assurance-policy', 'Menu', 336, 'This is a with profit plan that makes provisions for the family of the Life Assured in event of his early death and also assures a lump sum at a desired age on maturity. It costs moderate premiums, has high liquidity and in savings oriented.<br />\r\nThis plan is apt for people of all ages and social groups who wish to protect their families from a financial setback that may occur owing to their demise.', 'This is a with profit plan that makes provisions for the family of the Life Assured in event of his early death and also assures a lump sum at a desired age on maturity. It costs moderate premiums, has high liquidity and in savings oriented.<br />\r\nThis plan is apt for people of all ages and social groups who wish to protect their families from a financial setback that may occur owing to their demise.', 'Normal Group', 40, '2015-06-08', 'No', '344.jpg', 'normal', 'No', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(345, 'Jeevan Amrit', 'jeevan-amrit1', 'Menu', 336, '', '<p align="justify" style="margin: 0.35em 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">This plan is a combination of Endowment Assurance and Whole Life with profit plan. It provides financial protection against death throughout the lifetime of the life assured with the provision of payment of a lump sum at the maturity of the policy to the assured in case of his survival.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>Policy Requirements</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Minimum Entry Age&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : 16 Years</li>\r\n	<li>Maximum Entry Age &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : 65 Years</li>\r\n	<li>Maximum Maturity Age &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : 70 Years</li>\r\n	<li>Minimum Maturity Period&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : 5 Years</li>\r\n	<li>Maximum Maturity period &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : 25 Years</li>\r\n	<li>Minimum Sum Assured &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Rs. 50,000/-</li>\r\n	<li>Maximum Sum Assured &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Rs. 1,00,00,000/- (According to Income Source)</li>\r\n	<li>Premium Payment Frequency : Annually, Half Yearly, Quarterly and Monthly</li>\r\n	<li>Age computation&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Age next birthday</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Policy Benefits:</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Survival benefits:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sum Assured plus bonus earned shall be paid on maturity</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Death benefits:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sum Assured plus bonus earned shall be paid to the nominee</li>\r\n	<li>After maturity, Sum Assured shall be provided to the nominee on the death of assured</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>&nbsp;Rider Benefits:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Accidental Death Benefit (ADB) up to Rs. 2,500,000.00 in additional Rs. 1.00 per thousand.</li>\r\n	<li>Waiver of Premium (WOP) benefit shall be taken in additional Rs. 2.00 per thousand.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Other benefits:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Paid up and surrender claim shall be provided</li>\r\n	<li>Loan Facility provided.</li>\r\n	<li>Tax exemption as per ITA,2058</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Normal Group', 50, '2015-06-08', 'No', '345.jpg', 'normal', 'No', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(346, 'Anticipated Endowment Plan', 'anticipated-endowment-plan1', 'Menu', 336, '', '<span style="font-size:14px">This scheme provides for specific periodic payments of partial survival benefits during the term of the policy itself so long as the policy holder is alive. It is therefore suitable to meet specified financial requirements needed for occasions like Brata bandha, Academic Graduations etc.</span>\r\n<div align="justify">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<span style="font-size:14px"> An important feature of plan is that in the event of death at any time within the policy term, the death claim comprises full sum assured without deducting any of the survival benefit amounts, which have already been paid. It is also with profit plan.</span>', 'Normal Group', 60, '2015-06-08', 'No', '346.jpg', 'normal', 'No', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(347, 'Dampati Amrit Sawadhik Jeevan Beema', 'dampati-amrit-sawadhik-jeevan-beema1', 'Menu', 336, '', 'Under this Plan, life insurance risk coverage is provided for both husband and wife under single policy.<br />\r\n<strong>Policy Requirements</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Insured &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : &nbsp;Couple (Husband and Wife)</li>\r\n	<li>Minimum Entry Age &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;: 18 Years</li>\r\n	<li>Maximum Entry Age &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; : 60 Years</li>\r\n	<li>Maximum Maturity Age &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; : 65 Years</li>\r\n	<li>Age computation &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;: &nbsp;Nearest Age (Age nearest Birthday)</li>\r\n	<li>Minimum Maturity Period &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;: 5 Years</li>\r\n	<li>Maximum Maturity Period &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;: 30 Year</li>\r\n	<li>Minimum Sum Assured &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;: Rs. 50,000/-</li>\r\n	<li>Maximum Sum Assured &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; : According to income source of Husband and Wife</li>\r\n	<li>Premium payment frequency &nbsp; &nbsp;: Yearly, Half Yearly, Quarterly, Monthly</li>\r\n	<li>From Rs. 200,000.00 Sum Assured Rs. 1 rebate is provided</li>\r\n	<li>If the age difference between husband &amp; wife is more than 20 years, then &nbsp;they are not eligible for this plan</li>\r\n	<li>In this policy, both husband and wife have equal rights</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Survival Benefits: (Both insured or any one)</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sum assured plus bonus earned shall be paid on maturity</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Death Benefits:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>On death of any one of insured couple within the Insurance period, sum assured will be paid to living insured.</li>\r\n	<li>Premium payment shall be waived after the demise of an insured</li>\r\n	<li>On death of the another insured, the sum assured with earned bonus will be paid to nominated person within the policy term.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>&nbsp;Rider Benefits:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Accidental Death Benefit (ADB) up to Rs. 2,500,000.00 in additional Rs. 1.00 per thousand.</li>\r\n	<li>Waiver of Premium (WOP) benefit shall be taken in additional Rs. 2.00 per thousand.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Other benefits:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Paid up and surrender claim shall be provided</li>\r\n	<li>Loan Facility provided.</li>\r\n	<li>Tax exemption as per ITA,2058</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Normal Group', 70, '2015-06-08', 'No', '347.jpg', 'normal', 'No', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(348, 'Bachat Amrit Sawadhik Jeevan Beema Yojana', 'bachat-amrit-sawadhik-jeevan-beema-yojana1', 'Menu', 336, '', '<p style="margin: 0.35em 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>Special features:</strong></span><br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Policy issued under Endowment Life Assurance with profit plan<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Limited Premium paying term<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Fewer premiums charged with comparison to other endowment policies<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bonus is provided for full term year<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tax exemption facility as per Nepal Government rule<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Rebate on mode of payment which is not available in other plans<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Rs. 2 per thousand is provided for high sum assured<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>Policy Requirements</strong><br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Minimum entry age&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : 11 year<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Maximum entry age&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;: 55 year<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Maximum maturity age &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;: 70 year<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Age computation &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;: Age Next Birthday<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Term year&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;: 10 year, 15 year and 20 year<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Premium paying term year:&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0.35em 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size:14px">For 10 years only 8 year to be paid</span></li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0.35em 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size:14px">For 15 years only 12 year to be paid</span></li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0.35em 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size:14px">For 20 years only 16 year to be paid</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0.35em 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size:14px">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Minimum Sum Assured&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Rs. 50,000.00<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Maximum Sum Assured &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;: As per income source<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Premium Payment Frequency&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;: Yearly, Half-yearly and Quarterly<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Accidental Death Benefit&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;: Sum Assured or maximum up to Rs. 2,500,000.00<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Waiver of Premium &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;: can be included<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Rebate on mode of payment:&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0.35em 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size:14px">2% on Annual payment</span></li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0.35em 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size:14px">1% on Half Yearly payment</span></li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0.35em 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size:14px">5% loading on Quarterly (Additional)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0.35em 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size:14px">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;Rebate on Sum Assured:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0.35em 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size:14px">Rs. 1 per thousand from Rs. 100,000.00 to Rs. 300,000.00</span></li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0.35em 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size:14px">Rs. 2 per thousand above Rs. 300,000.00</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0.35em 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><strong>Benefits:</strong><br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; On maturity: Sum assured and accumulated bonuses are paid<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; In case of death: Sum Assured and accumulated bonuses are paid in case of unfortunate death of the assured during policy period before maturity date<br />\r\n<strong>Other benefits:</strong><br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;Surrender value&nbsp;&nbsp;: After completion of 2 years and as least 2 full years premium should have been paid from the date of commencement<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;Loan&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;: Maximum 90% of the Surrender value (Present Value)<br />\r\n<strong>Rider benefits:&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\nThere will be options to add Accidental Double Benefits (up to Rs. 2,500,000.00 Sum Assured) and Waiver of Premium (WOP) riders of customize the policy as per actual needs.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 'Normal Group', 80, '2015-06-08', 'No', '348.jpg', 'normal', 'No', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(349, 'Amrit Barsaha Money Back Policy', 'amrit-barsaha-money-back-policy1', 'Menu', 337, '', '<br />\r\nIt is a money back plan in a true sense and you get period specified percentage of sum assured during the policy term itself in a perfect proportionate manner. It is profit plan with bonus paid at maturity. Further, if the assured dies within the policy period, full sum assured is paid without deducting any installment which have already been paid. The plan is helpful to cover periodic expenses in the life of the assured.<br />\r\n<strong>Policy Requirements</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Minimum Entry Age : 18 Years</li>\r\n	<li>Maximum Entry Age : 55 Years</li>\r\n	<li>Maximum Insrurance Maturity Age : 70 Years</li>\r\n	<li>Policy Term : 7, 10,13,16,19,22 and 25 Years</li>\r\n	<li>Minimum Sum Assured: Rs. 50,000/-</li>\r\n	<li>Maximum Sum Assured: Rs. 100,00,000/-</li>\r\n	<li>Premium Payment Frequency: Yearly, Half Yearly, Quarterly, monthly</li>\r\n	<li>Age computation: Age next birthday</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Policy Benefit on Maturity</strong><br />\r\nPayment as following\r\n<table border="1" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="2" style="line-height:18px; width:349px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td align="center" colspan="8">Per thousand Premium Period</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td align="center">Term Policy</td>\r\n			<td align="center">4</td>\r\n			<td align="center">7</td>\r\n			<td align="center">10</td>\r\n			<td align="center">13</td>\r\n			<td align="center">16</td>\r\n			<td align="center">19</td>\r\n			<td>22</td>\r\n			<td align="center">25</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td align="center">7</td>\r\n			<td align="center">500</td>\r\n			<td align="center">500</td>\r\n			<td align="center">&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td align="center">&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td align="center">&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td align="center">&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td align="center">&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td align="center">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td align="center">